title: Chart - Autohide / hide numbers
text: To autohide the graph on the front of the POS: AutoHideChart = 1 To hide the numbers on the graph on the front of the POS: HideChartValue = 1
description:
To autohide the graph on the front of the POS: 

  

AutoHideChart = 1 

  

To hide the numbers on the graph on the front of the POS: 

  

HideChartValue = 1

title: Chart - shows different numbers on different POS
text: If a customer calls that the values or figures do not match on the POS, if they have more than one: The solution is 1. Write restart in the clerk field, press green button and wait for it to complete 2. Repeat the same for the next POS and so on if the shop has more than one POS. After the restart is done for all POS in the shop, check if they match. If there are still issues, try update chart. If this does not work, send the case to 2nd Line or Development.
description:
If a customer calls that the values or figures do not match on the POS, if they have more than one: 

  

 

  

  

  

  

The solution is  

  1. 1. Write restart in the clerk field, press green button and wait for it to complete 

  1. 2. Repeat the same for the next POS and so on if the shop has more than one POS. 

  

  

  

 

  

  

  

After the restart is done for all POS in the shop, check if they match. 

  

If there are still issues, try update chart.


If this does not work, send the case to 2nd Line or Development.
